  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The father broke the coconut and fell on his head, killing the son",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Namunukula police said that a coconut cut by the father fell on his son's head and the son died.",
        "A student named H.M. Samira who studied in the 10th grade of Mianakandura Maha Vidyalaya, who was a resident of Namunukula Mianakandura, has died.",
        "Recently (29th) at around 6.30 in the evening, when the father climbed a 50 feet high tree in the garden and broke a coconut, the police said that during the investigations, it was revealed that the son had left the house and was returning home and at that moment, a coconut cut by the father had fallen on the son's head. .",
        "The seriously injured deceased was being treated at Badulla General Hospital and passed away this morning (31st).",
        "The police also mentioned that legal action will be taken against the 55-year-old father under the charge of breaking coconut due to negligence."
      ],
